column1: Sex- indicates if crab is male or female
Frontal_lobe- Measures frontal lobe of crab (face/head)
Rear_width- Measures the width of backside of the crab (rear)
Carapace_length- Measures length of the carapace (shell) length
carapace width- measures width of carapace
body depth- measures thickness or the depth of the crab. Top of crab to bottom
Latitude- location at which crab was discovered
